策略一：减少输入Token**\\n- 压缩Prompt：去除冗余描述\\n- 上下文裁剪：只传相关内容\\n- 使用更短的系统提示\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**策略二：减少输出Token**\\n- 限制最大输出长度\\n- 要求简洁回答\\n- 使用结构化输出（JSON比叙述更短）\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**策略三：模型降级**\\n- 简单任务用小模型（如GPT-3.5）\\n- 复杂任务才用大模型\\n- 路由策略：根据问题复杂度选择模型\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**策略四：结果缓存**\\n- 缓存热门查询的结果\\n- 相似查询复用缓存\\n- 设置合理的缓存过期时间\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**策略五：批处理**\\n- 合并多个请求一次处理\\n- 减少API调用次数\\n- 利用批量折扣（如果有）\"}]]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]\n1c:T550,class ModelRouter:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.small_model = \"gpt-3.5-turbo\"\n        self.large_model = \"gpt-4\"\n        self.cache = {}\n\n    def route_query(self, query: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"根据问题复杂度选择模型\"\"\"\n        # 1. 检查缓存\n        cache_key = self._hash_query(query)\n        if cache_key in self.cache:\n            return self.cache[cache_key]\n\n        # 2. 分析问题复杂度\n        complexity = self._analyze_complexity(query)\n\n        # 3. 选择模型\n        if complexity < 0.3:\n            model = self.small_model  # 简单问题用小模型\n        elif complexity < 0.7:\n            model = self.small_model  # 中等问题也用小模型\n        else:\n            model = self.large_model  # 复杂问题用大模型\n\n        return model\n\n    def _analyze_complexity(self, query: str) -> float:\n        \"\"\"分析问题复杂度（0-1）\"\"\"\n        complexity = 0.0\n\n        # 关键词判断\n        complex_keywords = [\"分析\", \"对比\", \"推理\", \"为什么\", \"怎么理解\"]\n        for kw in complex_keywords:\n            if kw in query:\n                complexity += 0.2\n\n        # 长度判断\n        if len(query) > 100:\n            complexity += 0.2\n\n        # 多条件判断\n        if \"和\" in query or \"以及\" in query:\n            complexity += 0.1\n\n        return min(complexity, 1.0)15:[\"$\",\"div\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[